00:09:17.580 --> 00:09:22.959
Mike: I had two or three discs collapse, and
I couldn't walk right; I couldn't do anything.

00:09:22.960 --> 00:09:26.280
I was in horrible pain all the time.

00:09:26.280 --> 00:09:32.240
And I went to the chiropractors and I went
to the doctors, and they said, “You'll have

00:09:32.241 --> 00:09:33.241
to quit work.

00:09:33.241 --> 00:09:34.241
You can't work any more.

00:09:34.241 --> 00:09:38.300
You'll never work again”, this and that,
and all this gloom and doom, you know.

00:09:38.300 --> 00:09:43.490
I was working a construction job making great
money, $1,500 a week; back then and that was

00:09:43.490 --> 00:09:44.910
a lot of money.

00:09:44.910 --> 00:09:51.189
And I was just “macho”, and sport car,
you know, just winging it, having a good time,

00:09:51.189 --> 00:09:54.460
and like, finally, I'm not “Mr. Rejection”
anymore.

00:09:54.460 --> 00:09:56.280
“I’m worth something because I've got
some money”, you know.

00:09:56.280 --> 00:09:57.480
Sid: You also got some muscles.

00:09:57.480 --> 00:09:58.380
Mike: Yeah.

00:09:58.380 --> 00:10:01.300
I started to look better after awhile, you
know.

00:10:01.300 --> 00:10:04.760
And I wasn't - finally I was doing something
I wasn't failing at.

00:10:04.760 --> 00:10:06.800
I felt like a failure all my life.

00:10:06.800 --> 00:10:10.380
And now this came up, and I was just angry
again.

00:10:10.380 --> 00:10:18.140
So this Christian took me over to his house
one day and this man, his cousin, came in

00:10:18.140 --> 00:10:20.480
from New Orleans.

00:10:20.480 --> 00:10:24.800
And I was in his house, whining, “Oh, you
know, the doctors are saying ‘You'll never

00:10:24.800 --> 00:10:29.170
work again’”, and this and that, and I
was in pain, you know.

00:10:29.170 --> 00:10:33.209
And this guy walks up to me and he just looks
at me.

00:10:33.209 --> 00:10:36.519
He said, "Would you like Jesus to heal you?"

00:10:36.519 --> 00:10:40.970
And I looked at him and I said, "I'd like
anybody to heal me."

00:10:40.970 --> 00:10:44.820
But I says, "If Jesus can heal me, I'd like
that."

00:10:44.820 --> 00:10:46.040
It was selfish reasons.

00:10:46.040 --> 00:10:47.200
It wasn't - I wanted to know.

00:10:47.200 --> 00:10:48.320
Yeah, I wanted to be healed.

00:10:48.320 --> 00:10:49.740
I was hurting.

00:10:49.740 --> 00:10:51.180
Sid: What happened?

00:10:51.180 --> 00:10:54.220
Mike: He says "Well you kneel down here with
me and we'll pray for you."

00:10:54.220 --> 00:10:55.480
And I said, "I can't kneel down."

00:10:55.480 --> 00:10:58.660
So one guy on each arm and they set me down.

00:10:58.660 --> 00:11:03.040
And he walked up and put his hand on my back,
and he says, "Jesus, heal him."

00:11:03.040 --> 00:11:07.240
And instantly some heat went through my back.

00:11:07.240 --> 00:11:09.380
The pain quit.

00:11:09.380 --> 00:11:13.300
I looked at both of these guys and said, "This
is real."

00:11:13.300 --> 00:11:17.460
I got off the floor and I says, "Take me to
the gym."

00:11:17.460 --> 00:11:23.320
I went to the gym and I put a hundred more
pounds on than I had ever lifted, and I was

00:11:23.329 --> 00:11:24.550
picking stuff up.

00:11:24.550 --> 00:11:29.040
It was like when the Holy Ghost is on you,
you're a different person.

00:11:29.040 --> 00:11:32.280
And I was throwing weights all over the place,
and I'm on fire.

00:11:32.280 --> 00:11:34.540
And I kept - started thanking Jesus.

00:11:34.540 --> 00:11:35.320
“Thank you, Jesus.

00:11:35.320 --> 00:11:36.560
Thank you, Jesus”, you know.

00:11:36.560 --> 00:11:40.500
And they started taking me to church, all
through Kansas City and stuff, and I started

00:11:40.500 --> 00:11:41.180
witnessing.

00:11:41.180 --> 00:11:42.060
I wasn't saved.

00:11:42.060 --> 00:11:43.500
I wasn't nothing.

00:11:43.500 --> 00:11:48.200
I just know that God touched me, and I was
telling the church that Jesus heals.

00:11:48.200 --> 00:11:49.400
Sid: Jesus really does heal.

00:11:49.400 --> 00:11:52.720
Mike: Yeah. And I went to - oh, oh, I know it.

00:11:52.720 --> 00:11:56.140
Nobody can - you can tell me a lot of things
you may not think He does,

00:11:56.140 --> 00:12:00.939
but I know He heals, because he healed
me, and it's real, and it's never gone away.

00:12:00.940 --> 00:12:02.580
This has been 20 years almost.

00:12:02.580 --> 00:12:03.480
Sid: Okay.

00:12:03.480 --> 00:12:08.720
Tell me about the time you heard an audible
voice from God.

00:12:10.480 --> 00:12:15.620
Mike: The first time I heard an audible voice
was when I was doing cocaine in a crack house.

00:12:15.629 --> 00:12:20.740
In Kansas City there's this black brother,
and I used to go there.

00:12:20.740 --> 00:12:24.360
I was the only white man that could ever go
in the neighborhoods and be left alone.

00:12:24.360 --> 00:12:26.279
They never bothered me.

00:12:26.280 --> 00:12:32.860
And I was free-basing coke, and this voice
said, "Michael".

00:12:32.860 --> 00:12:38.520
And I looked up and it said, "Michael, I'm
not going to let you get high any more."

00:12:38.520 --> 00:12:41.980
And I knew it was God.

00:12:41.980 --> 00:12:44.780
I knew it was God.

00:12:44.780 --> 00:12:46.400
I says, "Garbage!"

00:12:46.400 --> 00:12:49.040
And I went and bought a hundred dollars' worth
of coke and free-based it.

00:12:49.049 --> 00:12:50.589
I couldn't get high.

00:12:50.589 --> 00:12:56.260
And I ran in the guy's front room, and I threw
a temper-tantrum on the guy's floor.

00:12:56.260 --> 00:12:57.220
Sid: Really?

00:12:57.220 --> 00:12:57.720
Mike: Yeah.

00:12:57.720 --> 00:13:02.780
This drug dealer is looking at me and I'm
throwing - and he says, "What's your problem?"

00:13:02.780 --> 00:13:05.020
I says, "God won't let me get high no more."

00:13:05.020 --> 00:13:10.220
And I was throwing a fit, so he run me off.

00:13:10.220 --> 00:13:17.960
And the time that was really impressive to
me, though, was when I decided I wanted to

00:13:17.960 --> 00:13:23.000
become a Christian, but I wanted to do it
on my terms. And uh –

00:13:23.000 --> 00:13:26.260
Sid: Well God has been pretty gracious to
you up until then.

00:13:26.260 --> 00:13:28.040
Mike: Oh, more than that.

00:13:28.040 --> 00:13:30.589
But you know, He picked me.

00:13:30.589 --> 00:13:35.959
I'm thankful for that because He wasn't going
to quit on me, and He knew everything that

00:13:35.959 --> 00:13:39.889
He allowed me to go through until the day
that He knew I was going to say yes.

00:13:39.889 --> 00:13:41.720
I know He knew that.

00:13:41.720 --> 00:13:44.160
Sid: So what happened on that day?

00:13:44.160 --> 00:13:48.869
Mike: I had been going to church and trying
to be a Christian.

00:13:48.869 --> 00:13:52.239
I saw some very honorable things, especially
what I saw in my wife.

00:13:52.240 --> 00:13:54.860
My wife is a woman of God.

00:13:54.860 --> 00:13:58.080
Boy, she's a jewel.

00:13:58.080 --> 00:14:01.639
And I wanted to be a Christian, but I didn't
trust God.

00:14:01.639 --> 00:14:02.790
I didn't trust anybody.

00:14:02.790 --> 00:14:03.790
I was afraid.

00:14:03.790 --> 00:14:04.790
“Is this real?”, you know?

00:14:04.790 --> 00:14:06.529
I didn't trust anything.

00:14:06.529 --> 00:14:10.740
So I tried to do it, and I tried to go through
the motions, but all this stuff was drawing

00:14:10.740 --> 00:14:12.600
me to other women.

00:14:12.600 --> 00:14:14.149
I wasn't married then.

00:14:14.149 --> 00:14:18.799
And it was drawing me back to this; it was
drawing me back to that; but God was still

00:14:18.800 --> 00:14:24.960
speaking to me and just - you could feel Him
tugging.

00:14:24.960 --> 00:14:27.980
So I didn't know what to do.

00:14:27.989 --> 00:14:33.369
I mean, you know, and then I was coming home
in the rush hour in Kansas City, and I had

00:14:33.369 --> 00:14:38.749
this beat-up Pinto station wagon with the
doors wired shut and the muffler is hanging

00:14:38.749 --> 00:14:39.840
off.

00:14:39.840 --> 00:14:42.000
And then the Lord spoke to me in an audible
voice.

00:14:42.000 --> 00:14:47.500
He says, "Michael, today I want you to give
me your heart."

00:14:49.060 --> 00:14:53.380
And I says, “No.”

00:14:53.380 --> 00:14:58.360
He says, "Today, give me your heart, or I
will lift my spirit off you and you'll go

00:14:58.360 --> 00:14:59.840
to Hell."

00:15:00.840 --> 00:15:02.200
Sid: Those are strong words.

00:15:02.200 --> 00:15:03.660
Hold that thought.

00:15:03.660 --> 00:15:05.200
We'll be back in just a moment.

00:15:05.200 --> 00:15:14.360
But what if God said to you, "Today, you must
give Me your heart, or you will go to Hell”?

00:15:14.360 --> 00:15:23.220
Do you realize that today could be the last
moment of your life?

00:15:23.220 --> 00:15:27.760
We'll be back in just a moment and find out
what happened to Michael.

00:15:27.760 --> 00:15:44.920
